import numpy as np
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

N = 50
x = np.random.rand(N)
y = np.random.rand(N)
colors = np.random.rand(N)
area = np.pi * (15 * np.random.rand(N))**2

plt.scatter(x,y, s=area, c=colors, alpha=0.5)
plt.show()
